posts.title: Palestine.
posts.description: Discover the rich history of Palestine, home to ancient cities like Jerusalem and cultural treasures such as traditional embroidery.

posts.title: Egypt
posts.description: Explore Egypt's wonders, from the majestic Pyramids of Giza to the vibrant markets of Cairo, a land of pharaohs and heritage.

posts.title: Saudi Arabia
posts.description: Experience Saudi Arabia's blend of modernity and tradition, with historic sites like Al Rajhi Grand Mosque and bustling Riyadh.

posts.title: Sudan
posts.description: Sudan captivates with its ancient Nubian pyramids and the vibrant culture along the Nile River, a hidden gem of Africa.

posts.title: Iraq
posts.description: Iraq, the cradle of civilization, boasts historic sites like Babylon and the vibrant heritage of Baghdad’s souks.
